This paper is about clustering algorithms, which are commonly studied in the machine learning and data mining fields (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM). The paper also introduces a new formulation of the type-2 fuzzy set, which is a topic in the fields of soft computing and computational intelligence (cs.SI, cs.NE).
